text: Ann Behrenfors (born 8 February 1961) is a Swedish equestrian. She competed in two events at the 1992 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1961 births Category:Living people Category:Swedish female equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of Sweden Category:Equestrians at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:People from Östergötland County
